video_title: Chandra Khatri - State of the Art in Agentic AI - SuperAI Singapore 2025
description:
Learn more about SuperAI: superai.com
Follow us on X: x.com/superai_conf

Keynote: State of the Art in Agentic AI: Building AI Agents for a Billion Voices

Speaker:
Chandra Khatri, Founding Head of AI @ Ola Krutrim

Stage: WEKA Stage
#superai #olakrutrim #aiagents #voiceai #ai

Recorded on 18 June 2025
